
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-savi-threat-scope-08.txt'>
    <title>"SAVI Threat Scope", Danny McPherson, Fred Baker, Joel Halpern</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-savi-threat-scope-08.txt</link>
    <description>Source Address Validation Improvement (SAVI) effort aims to complement ingress filtering with finer-grained, standardized IP source address validation.  This document describes threats enabled by IP source address spoofing both in the global and finer-grained context, describes currently available solutions and challenges, and provides a starting point analysis for finer-grained (host granularity) anti-spoofing work.</description>
    <dc:date>2013-04-08T22:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
